4.
Question 4
Why is Kotlin a preferred choice of language for Android mobile development compared to Java?
Ans--> Kotlin is interoperable or compatible with Java
       Kotlin is concise and time-saving
       Kotlin addresses common development issues with Java
       Kotlin code is easier to maintain

